question,answer
How do I reset my password?,You can reset your password by clicking the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and following the instructions sent to your email.
What are your business hours?,Our business hours are Monday through Friday from 9 AM to 6 PM EST. We're closed on weekends and major holidays.
How can I contact customer support?,You can reach our customer support team via email at support@company.com or by calling 1-800-123-4567 during business hours.
How do I track my order?,You can track your order by logging into your account and visiting the "Order History" section where you'll find tracking information for all your purchases.
What is your return policy?,We offer a 30-day return policy for all items in original condition. Please contact customer service to initiate a return.
How do I update my account information?,You can update your account information by logging in and going to "Account Settings" where you can modify your personal details and preferences.
Do you offer international shipping?,Yes we offer international shipping to most countries. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by location.
How do I cancel my order?,You can cancel your order within 1 hour of placing it by contacting customer service immediately. After that orders may have already been processed.
What payment methods do you accept?,We accept all major credit cards Paypal and bank transfers for your convenience.
How do I apply a discount code?,You can apply discount codes during checkout by entering the code in the "Promo Code" field before completing your purchase.